* Biomass was surprised that Perndabot hadn't made any move towards him by 
now, perhaps there was a thought or something in his programming that was 
holding him back. But it was his job to push buttons until he got the 
reaction he was looking for, and to see where Perndabot snapped was just 
that sort of reaction.
He glanced down towards Nue'e when Perndabot reacted to her, lifting a brow, 
realizing what she'd said before just now and giving Swift a side long 
clance.
Nue'e let go of Perndabot's finger after he had reacted to her, giving 
Biomass that look again and getting a look back that told her not to worry. 
She only sighed.
< Must be the new body.>
Biomass, narrowed his optics when he heard Perndabot's comeback, not feeling 
insulted but knowing that he wasn;t going to leave what he said without a 
responce. However, he could use the need to get to the Iron Fist as an 
excuse to push this man just a little further before he placed him under his 
concern and ignored him.
Biomass's expression turned aggressive.*

" You have a striking point there. So, I'll leave you women to your 
ammuseMENTS!" on the last word Biomass  struck to check his shoulder-plate 
hard against Perndabot's arm as he passed by, the force enough to knock even 
a bot Perndabot's size to the ground.
Biomass, on the other hand, continued walking towards the Iron Fist, leaving 
Nue'e to stand by Perndabot and stare at him in complete disbeliefe.*
